<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>سُورَةُ الدُّخَان<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تَفْسِيرُ السُّورَة<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{إِنَّا أَنْزَلْنَاهُ فِي لَيْلَةٍ مُبَارَكَةٍ , إِنَّا كُنَّا مُنْذِرِينَ , فِيهَا يُفْرَقُ كُلُّ أَمْرٍ حَكِيمٍ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٩٤:</span> <span class="c3">{يُفْرَقُ}</span>: يُفَصَّلُ ,<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> <span class="c3">{فَرَقْنَاهُ}</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>: فَصَّلْنَاهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [الدخان: ٣، ٤]<br>(٢) [الإسراء: ١٠٦]</p> </div>